<TEXT>
 <PERSON> Jim </PERSON> <PERSON> Abrams </PERSON> is <LOCATION> Beijing </LOCATION> bureau chief for <ORGANIZATION> The </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Associated </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Press </ORGANIZATION>.
