 <PERSON> Michael </PERSON> <PERSON> Putzel </PERSON> is chief of the <LOCATION> Moscow </LOCATION> bureau of <ORGANIZATION> The </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Associated </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Press </ORGANIZATION>.
